verbose_text: Those upregulated in the MON810 group (spot No. 1146, 1630) encoded three stress related proteins (catalase, 60 kDa heat shock protein and stress induced phosphoprotein 1), but again no-stress related proteins were upregulated in the commercial rodent diet group (Spot No. 2306 and 3258).
